data.description: Beautiful and very well maintained 2 bedroom, 2 bath Townhouse in small and quiet complex. Nice updated Kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances and closet pantry. Large living room with Fireplace. Large dining area.  Ceramic tile floors with carpet in bedrooms. Main bedroom has two closets, with extra storage. Vertical and mini blinds throughout. All appliances stay! Covered back patio has two storage sheds. The front yard in nicely landscaped. One covered parking area and a second uncovered spot. This Townhome is cute and move in ready!
